!theme plain
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 80

' --- STYLING (HIMS Blue Theme) ---
skinparam state {
 BackgroundColor #436FB6
 FontColor white
 BorderColor #2F528F
 FontSize 14
}
skinparam arrow {
 Color #2F528F
 FontColor #444444
 FontSize 11
}

title State Diagram: Complete Application Lifecycle

' --- STATES ---

state \"App Launched\" as Start
state \"System Error\" as Error

state \"Unauthenticated (Guest)\" as Guest {
 state \"Login Screen\" as Login
 state \"Registration\" as Register
 
 Login --> Register : Sign Up
 Register --> Login : Success
}

state \"Authenticated Session\" as Auth {
 
 state \"Role Check\" as Check <<choice>>
 
 state \"Driver Mode\" as Driver {
 state \"Dashboard (Idle)\" as D_Idle
 state \"Trip Active\" as D_Track
 
 D_Idle --> D_Track : Start Trip
 D_Track --> D_Idle : Stop Trip
 }
 
 state \"Passenger Mode\" as Passenger {
 state \"Search View\" as P_Search
 state \"Live Map\" as P_Map
 
 P_Search --> P_Map : Select Route
 P_Map --> P_Search : Close Map
 }
 
 state \"Admin Mode\" as Admin {
 state \"Fleet Dashboard\" as A_Dash
 state \"Data Entry\" as A_Edit
 
 A_Dash --> A_Edit : Manage
 A_Edit --> A_Dash : Save
 }
 
 ' Internal Routing
 Check --> Driver : [Role: Driver]
 Check --> Passenger : [Role: Passenger]
 Check --> Admin : [Role: Admin]
}

' --- TRANSITIONS ---

[*] --> Start
Start --> Guest : Open App

Guest --> Check : Login Success
Check --> Guest : Login Failed

' Global Logout Transitions
Driver --> Guest : Logout
Passenger --> Guest : Logout
Admin --> Guest : Logout

' Error Handling
Auth --> Error : Server Crash
Error --> Auth : Retry Connection
